give the Kings a 2-1 victory. Reuters; Photo, (Southland Edition) Linesman Gord 
Broseker restrains Calgary's Theoren Fleury during the first period Sunday 
night. JOSE GALVEZ / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
