-- CALIFORNIA; CALIFORNIA DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH SERVICES; HEALTH HAZARDS; 
TELEVISION COMMERCIALS; ADVERTISING AGENCIES; MINORITIES -- CALIFORNIA; 
CALIFORNIA -- WOMEN 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
