a warm, sunny day added to the pleasures of spring break. One student summed up 
the lure of the beach by calling it a matter of sun, fun and buns. Police said 
there was little trouble along the waterfront. Above, a street musician plays 
at Mission Beach. SEAN M. HAFFEY / For The Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
