<P>
IN THE STARS: ITALY VS. ARGENTINA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Wire Services 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
MILAN, Italy 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
After overnight occult rituals in the "very magic moment of the Aries 
plenilune, (full moon)" Italian clairvoyants today predicted that the World Cup 
final will pit Italy against defending champion Argentina. 
</P>
<P>
The prediction was made by wizards, astrologers and clairvoyants who are 
members of the Italian Wizards Assn. Some said they see an Italian victory. The 
clairvoyants also predicted that Cameroon and United Arab Emirates, both 
considered underdogs by experts, will do unexpectedly well. 
</P>
<P>
A dissident group, the "Wizards of the Hut," made different predictions. Its 
members see Brazil as the World Cup winner and Romania coming up with very 
interesting surprises. 
</P>
