<DATE>
<P>
April 10, 1990, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
HENRY KORN 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 3; Column 6; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
